# Never upload locally-generated, platform-specific build output — Vercel's
# own build regenerates these for its runtime (Linux). Uploading the Mac
# build alongside risked exactly the "wrong platform" bug this was added to
# prevent (see packages/db/prisma/schema.prisma binaryTargets comment).
packages/db/generated/
packages/*/dist/
apps/*/dist/
node_modules/
.next/
.turbo/
